```{r}
library(ggplot2)
files <- list.files(path = "outputs", pattern = ".csv", full.names = TRUE)

datasets <- c()

# files
for (f in files) {
  dataset <- read.csv(f)
  print(summary(dataset$TIMINGS))
  boxplot(dataset$TIMINGS,
    col = "Red", data = dataset, main = f,
    horizontal = TRUE
  )
  append(datasets, dataset)
}
```
